summary: The diff implements all five requirements (REQ-10 through REQ-14) comprehensively. The app is rebranded to 'Tribes Of Rudra' throughout, a full spiritual Hindu theme is applied, the FeedPage is enhanced with a landing page structure including all required sections, spiritual interest tags are updated on both Profile Setup and Discover pages, and the Feed page hero/post form copy is spiritually themed. No significant missing requirements or hallucinated features were identified.
